# Build context hygiene for the WATS Docker image.
# The builder stage reinstalls deps and rebuilds dist, so exclude them from the
# context to keep uploads small and reproducible. examples/ is kept because the
# root package.json declares it as a Bun workspace (install fails without it).
.git
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
docs
.hermes
*.log
*.pdf
*.tex
coverage
.DS_Store
